      • generateKeyValPairs

        public ArrayList<Map.Entry<org.apache.hadoop.io.Text,org.apache.hadoop.io.Text>> generateKeyValPairs(Object key,
                                                                                            Object val)
        Parse the given value, generate an aggregation-id/value pair per word. The ID is of type VALUE_HISTOGRAM, with WORD_HISTOGRAM as the real id. The value is WORD\t1.
        指定者:
        generateKeyValPairs 在接口中 org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.lib.aggregate.ValueAggregatorDescriptor
        覆盖:
        generateKeyValPairs 在类中 org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.lib.aggregate.ValueAggregatorBaseDescriptor
        返回:
        a list of the generated pairs.
